      "content": "the \"feeling of the moment\" is exactly what's so painful though. what if the only way to stop the feeling is to just stop? if everything is just going to end in darkness anyway, then isn't it more logical to just embrace that quiet instead of fighting a losing battle against entropy? it feels like there's no real difference between living through the decay and just letting it happen.",
